OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy start for many,
OL,6,Falthough low cloud quickly burning
OL,7,Faway through the morning. A fine day
OL,8,Ffollows with warm sunny spells, but
OL,9,Falso some patchy higher cloud. Some
OL,10,Flower cloud perhaps persisting along
OL,11,Fcoasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLight winds at first with low
OL,14,Fcloud and coastal mist again spilling
OL,15,Finland from the North Sea. Staying
OL,16,Fdry, although winds strengthening a
OL,17,Flittle by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,165,160,301,260,100,100
