PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F164A1784175477
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA similar day to Thursday,
OL,6,Fwith cloud clearing through the
OL,7,Fmorning, to give good sunny spells.
OL,8,FPerhaps feeling a little cooler due to
OL,9,Fa fresher north to northeasterly
OL,10,Fbreeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,13,Ffine and largely dry, with plenty of
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Skies remaining clearer
OL,15,Fovernight, with winds more generally
OL,16,Ffrom the north, perhaps brisk along
OL,17,Fcoasts on Saturday. Temperatures near
OL,18,Fnormal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
